title: Crispy Rosemary Potatoes
directions: Toss the potatoes with the oil, rosemary, and a generous amount of salt and pepper and spread out evenly on a baking sheet.
Roast until brown and crispy on the outside and tender inside, about 30 minutes.
ingredients: 1 1⁄2 lbs red potatoes, cut into 3⁄4" chunks
Salt and black pepper to taste
